File: Sports and Arts and Culture Minister, Nathi Mthethwa. (GCIS) JOHANNESBURG - Judge Zak Yacoob has recused himself as Chair of CSA Interim Board after a recording surfaced of Yacoob making derogatory remarks to a journalist. Sports Minister Nathi Mthethwa has appointed Stavros Nicolaou to take over. The decision for Yacoobs's recusal was by mutual agreement with Mthethwa.